
# [Linux From scrach](https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/lfs/read.html)
## step1 download source
```shell
./download-source.sh 
```
## step2 install docker engine
[docker install](https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/)
## step3 build and run docker container
```shell
./docker-run.sh
```

## step4 build image in docker container
```shell
docker exec -it lfs-121-systemd-lfs_service-1 bash
./step.sh
```
download and copy source of blfs to  sda.raw
```shell
./downloadSynchronize-beyong-source.sh
```


## step5 run qemu in docker container
```shell
./qemu-run.sh
```
in chroot-steps/compile-shadown-4.14.5.sh ,set user and password
username:root
passwd:root

## step6  compile and install blfs packages in guest os
```shell
/beyong-lfs-step.sh
```

